                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-122-off594 t17850914-122-cd595"></join> last, one leather trunk, value 25 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850914-122-victim1226" type="victimName">
                     James 
