                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-122-defend1224 t17850914-122-punish599"></join>
               confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
